  "comment": "SB220IP Stage Blinder IP65 WW/Amber: The IP65 rated SB220IP Stage Blinder is a powerful LED lighting fixture with a rugged aluminium design featuring Chip-on-Board (COB) LEDs that combines two effects in its housing. In addition to a standard stage blinder, this fixture can also be used as an authentic blinder effect. (Tungsten mode) The SB220IP matches the blinding light output of a conventional Audience Blinder and can be controlled in standalone mode or directly via DMX. The LEDs feature up to a 60.000 hour life expectancy.\n\n",
